header.gameNote: STATE FARM SUN BOWL TOURNAMENT AT EL PASO TX

article.headline: Drake 70, Toledo 52
article.story: EL PASO, Texas (AP) -- Ajay Calvin scored 17 points and grabbed nine rebounds to lead Drake to a 70-52 win over Toledo on Friday night in the Sun Bowl Tournament. Nick Grant added 10 points and six rebounds for the Bulldogs (8-2). Drake built a big lead in part because of its rebounding advantage. Six players grabbed at least four rebounds, including Aliou Keita and Jonathan Cox, who each had five. Drake had 44 total rebounds, compared to 26 for the Rockets (4-6). Florentino Valencia led Toledo with 15 points and five rebounds. Justin Ingram had 12 points.
